{"tid":719271,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"麥當勞三款平價包將加價1元","createTime":"2018-06-27T09:50:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T01:55:38.000Z","uid":181819,"like":2,"dislike":151,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c3a33378abe5ff7cbd64e87866ea32f848f07034","tid":719271,"uid":181819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T09:50:59.000Z","msg":"被網民形容為「窮人救星」的麥當勞三款平價包，豬柳蛋漢堡、雙牛芝堡及麥香雞，今日11時起將會由8元，加價1元，變成9元一個。 <br />\n<br />\n麥當勞發言人解釋，加價是由於營運成本如租金及食材價格不斷上漲，又指今次只是調整了這三款漢堡價格，其他產品價格不變。 <br />\n<br />\n早前網上已有自稱是麥當勞的職員放風，預告三款平價包將加價1元，不少網民都指麥記搶錢，慨嘆以後「冇8蚊平包買」。 <br />\n<br />\n中文大學市場學系教授冼日明指，麥記今次挑選三款平價包加價，生活艱難的基層市民首當其衝。他又預計麥當勞其他售價較平的「超值選」產品很快會加價。"},{"pid":"d3bacec6732d11320c1836bc5c48833ad5853369","tid":719271,"uid":37733,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T09:53:11.000Z","msg":"幾年前牙"},{"pid":"2d71ee4ccb3beefb99592b68baf65e1aab0b8dd0","tid":719271,"uid":18366,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T09:55:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1596df6b1ad576be5c287a9af8368b47a139c52d","tid":719271,"uid":5499,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T09:55:45.000Z","msg":"( Show Blocked User - 什麼我都有預感 )"},{"pid":"499a21d4e6befc7bf26d1623aab9f071e0b89fd4","tid":719271,"uid":35468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T09:57:20.000Z","msg":"8蚊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾多年前"},{"pid":"b6de3b684a1b21e4a3f0a03eb2438b47fcb4a096","tid":719271,"uid":181819,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T10:16:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1edb3ed864473f6eb93aad68aad84aba22abc93","tid":719271,"uid":119008,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"1596df6b1ad576be5c287a9af8368b47a139c52d","tid":719271,"uid":5499,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T09:55:45.000Z","msg":"( Show Blocked User - 什麼我都有預感 )"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T10:17:42.000Z","m